  "title": "Construction Manager (New Viaducts)/ 5day/Upto $13K basic+Bonus/ A1 maincon",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Participating in new LTA project [Viaduct and Station]</strong><br>\n<strong>• Having experience in LTA project [Viaduct and Station] is mandatory.</strong><br>\n<strong>•Permanent role/ 5 workdays/ West area </strong><br>\n<strong>• MNCs &amp; leading A1 main contractor</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Project Planning &amp; Execution:</strong>Develop and execute comprehensive project plans, ensuring alignment with timelines, budgets, and quality standards.<br>\nOversee day-to-day operations, including manpower allocation, construction progress monitoring, scheduling, and cost control.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Risk Management &amp; Issue Resolution:</strong>Proactively address project challenges, such as delays, emergencies, and site issues.<br>\nCollaborate effectively with clients, consultants, subcontractors, authorities, and developers to resolve issues and ensure compliance.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Resource Optimization:</strong>Optimize resource utilization through effective manpower planning, work scheduling, and cost management.<br>\nControl expenses related to materials, labor, and machinery for both new and ongoing projects.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Quality &amp; Safety Assurance:</strong>Implement safe and efficient construction methodologies.<br>\nEnforce project standards and ensure compliance with safety regulations.<br>\n</li>\n  <li><strong>Other:</strong>Perform additional duties as assigned.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br>\n• Degree in Civil Engineering and/or relevant field<br>\n• experience in LTA project [Viaduct and Station] is mandatory.</p>\n<p><strong>To apply, please include the following details inside your resume:</strong><br>\n• Reasons for leaving each past &amp; current employment<br>\n• Salary drawn for each past &amp; current employment<br>\n• Expected Salary<br>\n• Earliest availability date</p>\n<p><strong>How to apply</strong><br>\nInterested candidates who wish to apply for the position, you may send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\">search84@searchindex.com.sg</a></p>\n<p><strong>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly.</strong><br>\n<strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p>\n<p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong><br>\n<strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
